    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Mengakibatkan 2 poin </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_6493938593197331036.png",
                "id": "talent17041",
                "key": "Whirlwind Thrust",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Whirlwind Thrust"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/775a72af4465a157d3769ee561744b61_9115580297038727458.png",
                "id": "talent33932",
                "key": "Lemniscatic Wind Cycling",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Lemniscatic Wind Cycling"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 4 poin<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\"> Anemo DMG</span>. Karakter ini memperoleh status <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Yaksha's Mask</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Yaksha's Mask</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span> yang diakibatkan oleh Karakter diubah menjadi <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG </span>dan mengakibatkan <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span> +1.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Saat Karakter melancarkan Plunging Attack:</span> Mengakibatkan DMG +2 tambahan.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Saat Karakter digunakan sebagai Karakter aktif dan melakukan aksi \"bertukar Karakter\":</span> Mengonsumsi 1 Dadu Elemental lebih sedikit. (Sekali setiap Ronde) </p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Durasi (Ronde): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/447838f91bec368a2772f63aaa927c4c_2655926442842589356.png",
                "id": "talent46385",
                "key": "Bane of All Evil",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Bane of All Evil"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Bereaksi dengan Elemen jika sudah diberikan:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Cryo DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Hydro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Electro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_8516972311026777902.png",
                "id": "talent31330",
                "key": "Anemo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Anemo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Plunging Attack</span></strong></p><p>Setelah berganti ke Karakter Aktif, jika Aksi Tempur berikutnya di Ronde ini adalah Normal Attack, maka akan dianggap sebagai Plunging Attack.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span></strong></p><p>Setiap kali kamu mencapai Tahap Selesai di setiap Ronde, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> -1.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> habis.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_5438224528855552772.png",
                "id": "talent48091",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
